mod_ferite - the apache webserver ferite module

This README has been shamelessly stolen from mod_perl

Apache version 2.0.36 or higher is required.

ferite version 1.0.0 or higher is required.

Only DSO build of mod_ferite is currently supported, static builds
will be support in the future if there is demand for it.

For comments, questions, bug-reports, etc. please send by email
to ferite@centiongroup.com

mod_ferite was designed and written by the people mentioned
in AUTHORS

-------------------------------------------------------------

Please make sure you have the apr development files installed.

The best way to install into a distribution apache2 is to specify --with-apxs
